727952f-a.title: Queens: St. Nicholas Avenue - Woodbine Street
727952f-a.text:
St. Nicholas Ave., north side, west of Woodbine Street. Note,white
stuccoed structures at richt extending to Palmetto Street (elevated line
thereon) are on site of old carbarns and are now known as the Ridgewood
Grove, s place of amusepment..
September 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
